<paragraph id="4A6336F3FFE3FFA2FC959BE06C767A9C" blockId="14.[831,1436,1956,2077]" pageId="14" pageNumber="28">
<emphasis id="78A8EAE1FFE3FFA2FC959BE06ABD7ADD" bold="true" box="[831,944,1956,1980]" pageId="14" pageNumber="28">Remarks:</emphasis>
This species is characterized by its rapid expansion toward the apertural end and by its broad convex apertural face as identified by LE ROY (1953).
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="4A6336F3FFE3FFA2FCEA94416C91757C" blockId="14.[831,1436,1956,2077]" box="[832,1436,2053,2077]" pageId="14" pageNumber="28">
