</paragraph>
<paragraph id="4A6336F3FFE2FFA3FF3D9D4568327CD6" blockId="15.[151,756,257,439]" pageId="15" pageNumber="29">
this species only from his Maastrichtian unit “A” but it seems to have a longer range (Paleocene age) as referred by SAID &amp; KENAWY (1956). In the study area, the 
<taxonomicName id="8DDC4D70FFE2FFA3FF3D9D2468A27C19" box="[151,431,352,376]" class="Globothalamea" family="Spiroplectamminidae" genus="Spiroplectammina" kingdom="Chromista" order="Lituolida" pageId="15" pageNumber="29" phylum="Foraminifera" rank="species" species="knebeli">
